'''Rusty Goffe''' is an actor who was a contract artiste for the [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina|cantina]] scene in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV A New Hope'']].<ref name="Making of" />

He also later worked with [[George Lucas]] on the [[1988]] film [[Willow (film)|''Willow'']], in which he had an uncredited role as a Nelwyn villager.

